Nigerian rapper and actor, Ikechukwu Killz has shared a recovery update on Instagram, months after getting fans worried over his state following a social media post where he claimed he wasn’t ‘okay’. Ikechukwu took to his Instagram page to share a video of him on crutches as he attempted stretching his muscles. He captioned the post; Slowly but surelyI will get back walking .I will touch my toes without bending my knees.I will feel no sharp stabs in my back or legs .I will do back flip in February.  All the things I took for granted by letting my regular practices fall off.Never again as God is my witness and healer. I dey come  P.s. I will also gain the weight back Watch the videos below… ???? A post shared by Lindaikejiblog (@lindaikejiblogofficial)